Story:
Military Forces have recieved intelligence of an underground cell developing within this market district. The CT's Job is too assualt/infilitrate their makeshift base located below the streets of the nieghborhood. Enterances can be found within most of the residences homes and also through other means.

Once inside the base the CT's are to either eliminate there entire force removing the threat or blow up there collection of weapons or communications gear so as too not alert other cells of their capture.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Level layout, 4 floors total,
~Street Level
~Rooftop areas
~Tunnels SB1
~Tunnels SB2

Time Of Day: Late Night or Dusk
